    {
      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<div class=\"portlet-boundary portlet-boundary_56_ portlet-borderless portlet-journal-content  portlet-draggable yui3-dd-drop\" id=\"p_p_id_56_INSTANCE_MwUzo4Nk1sL6_\">\n<div class=\"portlet-body\" id=\"aui_3_4_0_1_1434\">\n<div class=\"portlet-borderless-container\" id=\"aui_3_4_0_1_1433\">\n<div class=\"portlet-body\" id=\"aui_3_4_0_1_1432\">\n<div class=\"journal-content-article\" id=\"article_1_3133562_74873912_1.7\">\n<p>Delivering fixes is one of the essential services included with your Liferay Enterprise Subscription. For Liferay DXP, we have designed our fix delivery method to match your project phase so you have ongoing access to the latest updates. Use the chart below as well as the definitions that follow to better understand how we provide fixes for Liferay DXP.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"portlet-boundary portlet-boundary_56_ portlet-borderless portlet-journal-content  portlet-draggable yui3-dd-drop yui3-dd-draggable\" id=\"p_p_id_56_INSTANCE_PKoSfgd0ZWqC_\"><span id=\"p_56_INSTANCE_PKoSfgd0ZWqC\"></span>\n\n<div class=\"portlet-body\" id=\"aui_3_4_0_1_1467\">\n<div class=\"portlet-borderless-container\" id=\"aui_3_4_0_1_1466\">\n<div class=\"portlet-body\" id=\"aui_3_4_0_1_1465\">\n<div class=\"journal-content-article\" id=\"article_1_3133562_75158827_2.2\">\n<h2 id=\"h_01H9PCP3ZFXQD6TF520HV1BVAE\"><a href=\"#development\" id=\"development\">Development Phase: Maintenance Releases</a></h2>\n\n<p>Maintenance Releases are periodically released for every Liferay DXP component. Included in these releases are a collection of fixes that are carefully selected and uphold the quality and stability of the product by resolving known issues. Maintenance Releases undergo extensive QA testing and introduce significantly less risk than an Emergency Update. They represent the most current code base, and since Liferay focuses on resolving known issues in the current code base, we recommend that you stay up to date with the latest Maintenance Release during your project's development phases.</p>\n\n<p id=\"aui_3_4_0_1_1464\">For the core modules and suites that are part of Liferay Digital Experience Platform, Maintenance Release will be released as a fix pack or release through Customer Portal. For other Liferay components and Marketplace apps, updates will be periodically available through the Liferay Marketplace or Customer Portal.</p>\n\n<table class=\"table table-autofit table-list table-nowrap\" style=\"width: 697px; border-collapse: collapse;\">\n\t<thead>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Estimated Release Targets</span></th>\n\t\t\t<th style=\"background-color: rgb(247, 248, 249); padding: 10px; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); text-align: center;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Regular</span></th>\n\t\t\t<th style=\"background-color: rgb(247, 248, 249); padding: 10px; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); text-align: center;\"><font size=\"2\">As Needed</font></th>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</thead>\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: left; vertical-align: top; padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Liferay DXP*</span></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid #ddd; color: #28a745; font-size: 1.2em;\">✔</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid #ddd; color: #28a745; font-size: 1.2em;\">✔</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: left; vertical-align: top; padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Liferay Commerce</span></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid #ddd; color: #28a745; font-size: 1.2em;\">✔</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid #ddd; color: #28a745; font-size: 1.2em;\">✔</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: left; vertical-align: top; padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Liferay Developer Tools**</span></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid #ddd;\">&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid #ddd; color: #28a745; font-size: 1.2em;\">✔</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: left; vertical-align: top; padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Liferay Frameworks***</span></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid #ddd;\">&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid #ddd; color: #28a745; font-size: 1.2em;\">✔</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">* Core Modules and Suites (Static, Foundation, Web Experience, Collaboration, Forms and Workflow)</span><br>\n<span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">** Liferay Developer Studio, Blade CLI, Liferay Workspace, Liferay Maven</span><br>\n<span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">*** Liferay Faces, Lexicon, etc.</span></p>\n\n<h2 id=\"h_01H9PCP3ZGAMN4C054RWTWMSB8\"><a href=\"#production\" id=\"production\">Production Phase: Emergency Updates</a></h2>\n\n<p>Emergency Updates are provided on a case-by-case basis for Liferay components that are deployed on production environments. If your Production deployment schedule limits the amount of changes you can make to your Production environments, or their frequency, we recommend that you request Emergency Updates from the Liferay Support Team. These updates are customer-specific temporary solutions that will be included in future Maintenance Updates. For Liferay Digital Experience Platform, Emergency Updates are also known as hotfixes which are short-term solutions that can patch the core modules and suites. If you have installed Emergency Updates, we highly recommend that you bring your Liferay DXP system up to date with the latest Maintenance Updates, as soon as you enter a new Development Phase.</p>\n\n<table class=\"table table-autofit table-list table-nowrap\" style=\"width: 675px; border-collapse: collapse;\">\n\t<thead>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Estimated Release Targets</span></th>\n\t\t\t<th style=\"background-color: rgb(247, 248, 249); padding: 10px; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); text-align: center;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Regular</span></th>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</thead>\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: left; vertical-align: top; padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Liferay DXP</span></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid #ddd; color: #28a745; font-size: 1.2em;\">✔</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: left; vertical-align: top; padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Liferay Commerce</span></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid #ddd; color: #28a745; font-size: 1.2em;\">✔</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: left; vertical-align: top; padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Liferay Developer Tools*</span></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid #ddd;\">&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: left; vertical-align: top; padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Liferay Frameworks**</span></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid #ddd;\">&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">* Liferay Developer Studio, Blade CLI, Liferay Workspace, Liferay Maven<br>\n** Liferay Faces, Lexicon, etc.&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<h2 id=\"h_01H9PCP3ZHDTFPDG5XBCZWZDP3\"><a href=\"#additional\" id=\"additional\">Additional Information</a></h2>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li><a href=\"/w/recommended-patching-cycle-for-liferay-dxp-customers\" target=\"_self\">Recommended Patching Cycle for Liferay DXP Customers</a></li>\n\t<li><a href=\"https://learn.liferay.com/kb-article/patch-management-best-practices\" target=\"_self\">Patch Management Best Practices</a></li>\n\t<li>To access Releases, Fix Packs, Service Packs, Patching Tool, and Security Releases, visit our <a href=\"https://customer.liferay.com/downloads\" target=\"_self\">Downloads</a> page</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div class=\"article-content\">\n<section class=\"article-body\">\n<article id=\"aui_3_4_0_1_1358\">\n<p>Please subscribe to our<span>&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.subscribepage.com/liferay\" target=\"_self\">Liferay Support Updates</a>&nbsp;to stay informed on the latest releases.</p>\n</article>\n</section>\n</div>\n\n<footer class=\"article-footer\">&nbsp;</footer>"
